This paper discusses the design of a new index structure for multi-version databases, which is relevant to the database community (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the impact of the index structure on I/O patterns, which is relevant to the distributed systems community (cs.DS) and the computer architecture community (cs.DC). The paper proposes a new data structure, which is a contribution to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
